eu.planets_project.TB.api.interfaces.model
Interface ExperimentSetup

All Superinterfaces:
ExperimentPhase
public interface ExperimentSetup
extends ExperimentPhase

The phase ExperimentSetup covers the steps of 1-3 of the Planets Testbed process model. Step 1 define basic properties; Step 2 design the experiment's workflow (= services, data, configuration) Step 3 specify ressources
